Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade in a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:37.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:41.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:17.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You still can’t get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:02:00.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You show up after all this time,\Nand this is what I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You could’ve said something nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:09.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve already recovered.\NI’m able to fight any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:17.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now it’s your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get off your back\Nand get well, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:25.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And let us fight that\NZangetsu bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The next time for sure, I’ll…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I’ll win!\N– ...win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:40.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fool…\NWere you asleep, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:45.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s no longer the one I must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:50.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then who must you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who will you fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:28.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before it goes to your head,\NI’ll show you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This power gap that\Nyou’ll never bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,not in a thousand years…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, Ichigo! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:54.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a long time, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:00.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi Shihoin…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she? I don’t know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:11.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve heard that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:15.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:21.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Former Commander of\Nthe Stealth Force and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:25.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of Squad One\NPunishment Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi Shihoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven’t seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve been in hiding for\Nover a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:37.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You came to rescue me, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to defeat this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You? Defeat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:08.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What’re you doing…\NYoru…i…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Gaten” or “hoten.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:26.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You thrust a powerful anesthetic\Ndirectly into him, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:31.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do\Nwith him, Yoruichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you do will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no escaping from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:44.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… You talk like a big shot now,\Ndon’t you? Byakuya boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:49.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever once\Nbeaten me at “tag”?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:23.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could escape\Nwith such a slow Flash Step?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:43.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could capture me\Nwith such a slow Flash Step?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In three days,\NI’ll make this boy stronger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:56.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This fight is postponed until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give chase, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Flash Master” Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:04.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,won’t be caught by the likes of you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They got away…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:21.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:23.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where’re you going, Byakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you come to capture\Nthe ryoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:37.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, he’s as willful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:48.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The tension drained out of her\N when Byakuya left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:54.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sentaro! Kiyone!\NCome out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You called, Captain, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:10.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you did follow me.\NHow long were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the time you said,\N“My, my, how dangerous,”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and stopped Captain Kuchiki,\NCaptain, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the very start, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t I tell you not to come\Nbecause it was dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:28.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I respect you so very much,\Nthat I simply had to follow you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Kotsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I feel the same! I love y…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No…! I respect you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-h?! I respect him much,\Nmuch more than you, by far!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-ah?! Shut up, Mt. Fuji-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight, booger-face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:57.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, Kiyone, contact 4th Squad.\NOne apprehended. Wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Send for an advanced relief squad ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, you take Kuchiki\Nback to the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:13.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:17.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I can’t let Rukia\Ngo back in there…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Damned booger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:25.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think I’m doing this\Nbecause I want to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kuchiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The captain and I will appeal to\Nthe top brass afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:41.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and get you out of the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Kotsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I worry much, much more\Nabout Kuchiki than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:57.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, the captain and I will promise,\Npromise to get you out, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:10:00.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep copying what I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight, copycat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You hurry up and call 4th Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I was just about to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:25.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know why\NI’m helping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I’ll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t know who killed Aizen yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:35.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And it’s very likely that you outsiders\Nknow something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t kill you without\Ninvestigating first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And above all else…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though your methods were bad,\Nyou tried to rescue my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one back there, either, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:16.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You men take the East Nijo area!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ryoka are cunning!\NDon’t lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the report!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:28.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never seen you two before.\NAre you new?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:34.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We joined this period! I’m Inoue!\NPlease remember me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:38.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Ishida. Please…remember me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My word…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya say?\NWhy not come to my place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:58.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must’ve heard of me.\NToshimori Umesada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This year, I made 15th\Nin the 20-seat Ninth Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I’m boasting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I’m the most successful\Nof all my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:09.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll treat you good…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:16.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When ryoka have infiltrated,\Nand a wartime alert has been issued,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly think a squad leader\Nhas time for propositioning women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:25.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You lowly underling!\NYou dare lecture me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Umesada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing here, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awaiting further instructions, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once this commotion is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna give it to you good!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By then, I’ll be long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:50.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn’t much…\NI just dislike his type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still, how incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:55.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I wasn’t that great…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It worked out beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Steal the Soul Reapers’ clothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Not so loud, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re just going to borrow\Ntheir clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Appearance-wise,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we’re not so different\Nfrom Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only our clothes are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:23.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we can look like them,\Nwe’ll be able to get around more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So we need their clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we’re borrowing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I say, “Go,” okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:41.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh…I forgot to jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…! Here, your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You knocked those two out\Nwithout using your spirit powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re surprisingly strong, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Eh, heh, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:04.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I learned a little karate\Nfrom Tatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:05.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:09.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She said I had the skills of\Na first-level student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:15.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. We’d better get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait! Wait, Ms. Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…I see. Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boys and girls can’t dress\Nin the same room, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like I was with Tatsuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:30.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…well… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:38.53,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Ishida’s Special Dressing Room”\N“Comfy” “Spacious”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:41.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn’t it be the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida! Ready? Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:49.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got those two to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:56.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,about the Senzaikyu where\NKuchiki is being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The others must already\Nbe headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:06.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kurosaki…\NHe might already have gotten there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. We’d better hurry, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:17.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve got to help him\Nbefore he screws up, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:19.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What squad shall\Nwe say we’re from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:28.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to answer quickly\N if we’re asked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…you’re right…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:12.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it’s because\NI haven’t fought in a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:16.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m breathing hard after\Nonly a hundred Flash Steps or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How weak I’ve grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you’re awake, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:43.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why’d you bring me back alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:05.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one with the best chance\Nof surviving back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now Ganju, Hanataro,\Nand Rukia will all be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be so vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:15.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one back there had\Nany chance against Byakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be still! Do you want to open up\Nthose wounds again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go…to…hell…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:38.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One person was all I could carry\Nand get away from Byakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:41.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn’t you take Rukia\Ninstead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:44.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,True…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:51.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, no one there had\Nany chance of defeating Byakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you alone have the ability to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I brought you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:03.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Ukitake was there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:07.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s Rukia’s superior,\Nwith a strong sense of obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though you’re insurgents,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:12.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he’d never blindly kill anyone\Nwho came to save Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:17.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ichigo, don’t worry.\NGrow strong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As you are now,\Nyou’d never defeat Byakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ll train you so that you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:27.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then go back and rescue everyone\Nwith your own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How’s the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s much better than earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t wait for you\Nto recover completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It might hurt, but you must do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno if I’ve seen this place before…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:52.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the first outsider\NI’ve ever brought here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:55.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huhh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:56.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time’s short, right? Let’s get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:02.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Now…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First, are you aware that\Nyour zanpaku-to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:10.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is already in released mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Released mode,\Nlike Kenpachi Zaraki’s…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:22.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder its shape was different\Nfrom other people’s swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And it never transformed\Nwhen I called its name…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. You weren’t aware of it,\Nafter all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:34.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you don’t know Zangetsu\Ncan be released to another level?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:35.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Zangetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:42.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All zanpaku-to swords\Ncan be released to two levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:47.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The first release is called “Shikai.”\NThe second release is “Bankai.”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To perform these two releases,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that’s a requirement for\Nsquad captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:56.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Requirement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:04.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,all squad captains of the Court Guard\Nhave mastered “Bankai.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:04.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenpachi Zaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the vast history of\Nthe Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:15.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he’s about the only one to\Nbecome captain without achieving “Bankai”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:19.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or even knowing the name\Nof his zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:24.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It shows how greatly the\N13 Court Guard Squads must value
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:27.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,his fighting prowess and tenacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:32.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Having fought him,\Nyou should know that best of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:43.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The difference in power between\Nthe Shikai and Bankai levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,though dependent on\Neach fighter’s ability and discipline,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,can be considered roughly\Nfive to ten times greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ten times…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An amazing increase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:59.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why, in order to achieve\N“Bankai,”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:02.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even strong fighters train\Nfor over 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I ain’t got time…!\N– I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:09.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be pretty dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:17.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you’ll use a completely different method\Nand master “Bankai” in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:37.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stand up! Everybody fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:49.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Within your heart, you may feel uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But keep your head right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:57.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:21:59.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:02.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me anytime! (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:08.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:11.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With a tough smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:17.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:20.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:22.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:26.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:36.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, what squad shall\Nwe say we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does each squad have\Na unique characteristic?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:39.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:42.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like a squad that loves flowers,\Nor a musical squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:43.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or a squad that tells great jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:46.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, you don’t understand\Na Soul Reaper’s work, do you?